 But Disney Culture encompasses much more than just movies as it explores the intersections between Disney’s business practices and its cultural mythmaking. Welcome to “the Disney Way.”   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Jan 2021) 0aCorporate culture. 4abusiness. 4aconsumer culture. 4acorporation. 4adisney corporation. 4adisney. 4aespn. 4afantasia. 4aforce awakens. 4afrozen. 4alucasfilm. 4amarvel. 4amary poppins. 4apixar. 4astar wars. 4awalt disney. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertRUP eBook-Package 2017z978311066609040uhttps://doi.org/10.36019/978081358334140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780813583341423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780813583341.jpg  a978-3-11-066609-0  RUP eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK